		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hmm, what do you think is the hardest routine to come up with? The hardest I've encountered is this one, definitely. Another one that took me a while, even though it's not hard at all compared to this, was a routine that would take a sequence of tiles and make it into a 16 byte array. It's on <a href="http://www.freewebs.com/the_bott/gedit.nes" class="postlink">this graphics editor</a> that I made. One routine takes the 16 byte array that makes the tile and turns it into a sequence of tiles. That wasn't as hard as taking the tiles, and turning them into a 16 byte array. Do you know what I'm saying? If not, use the graphics editor, and you'll get an idea of what I'm talking about.

		

