		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I coded a routine to convert a 256-byte array into 4 16-byte tiles and output them to the pattern tables. Are you talking about something like that?
<br />
<br />I needed this because my decompression routine did a 16x16-pixel square at a time using 8 bits per pixel, for easy indexing. When the square was ready, it had to be converted and exported as 4 individual tiles, with separated planes and all the shit a NES expects.
<br />
<br />Celius, I think your program is interesting. I'll leave some comments on it's thread.

		

